    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >波斯地区的人口繁盛，资源丰富，常常是帝国的重要十字路口。购买《Crusader Kings III》全新特色包《Legacy of Persia》，回到风情万种的历史战略重地波斯，参与中世纪的权力斗争。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >公元9世纪，阿拔斯王朝迎来历史性崩溃，萨马拉陷入混乱之中，《Legacy of Persia》便从中汲取灵感，上演各大势力角逐此地的“伊朗间奏曲”。以《Fate of Iberia》特色包的斗争系统为基础，《Legacy of Persia》为该地区的领地王国加入更多重要的文化要素和变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Crusader Kings III: Legacy of Persia》的特色包含：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313540/extras/a76192b190ce949c4dbe11c0dd577c86.poster.avif?t=1765207386\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313540/extras/a76192b190ce949c4dbe11c0dd577c86.webm?t=1765207386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313540/extras/a76192b190ce949c4dbe11c0dd577c86.mp4?t=1765207386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >伊朗间奏曲：阿拔斯王朝日暮西山，意志坚定的伊朗统治者决心实现该地区的独立，开创新的未来。是建立新帝国，为本国利益征服摇摇欲坠的哈里发王朝，还是复兴哈里发王朝，让该地区恢复正常秩序？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313540/extras/8a6650f09a6b8e324dce753858f46f08.poster.avif?t=1765207386\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313540/extras/8a6650f09a6b8e324dce753858f46f08.webm?t=1765207386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313540/extras/8a6650f09a6b8e324dce753858f46f08.mp4?t=1765207386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更浓厚的历史特色：波斯地区的领袖获得新决议、新互动、新建筑，更有强调家族领导和边境地区保护重要性的特别内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313540/extras/d850927696053f9458f79442a2f50ce7.poster.avif?t=1765207386\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313540/extras/d850927696053f9458f79442a2f50ce7.webm?t=1765207386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313540/extras/d850927696053f9458f79442a2f50ce7.mp4?t=1765207386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >伊朗文化变迁：伊朗形成新传统，包括富有创新精神的王庭学者、独特的披甲战士、以及能在贫瘠土地上创造财富的强力新建筑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313540/extras/3539da49c7a89c575c239235b6548af1.poster.avif?t=1765207386\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313540/extras/3539da49c7a89c575c239235b6548af1.webm?t=1765207386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313540/extras/3539da49c7a89c575c239235b6548af1.mp4?t=1765207386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全新美术和音乐：在本特色包中，波斯角色换上新衣，波斯建筑得到重新设计，游戏用户界面更能体现伊朗格调。还有8首全新音乐曲目，或暗示历史事件，或烘托游戏氛围。</p>",
